article.description: — AJ George's 18 points helped Long Beach State defeat CSU Bakersfield 79-66 on Thursday.
article.headline: George leads Long Beach State over Cal State Bakersfield 79-66
article.linkText: George leads Long Beach State over Cal State Bakersfield 79-66
article.story: LONG BEACH, Calif. -- — AJ George's 18 points helped Long Beach State defeat CSU Bakersfield 79-66 on Thursday. George had seven rebounds for the Beach (18-9, 10-5 Big West Conference). Lassina Traore scored 15 points with six rebounds. Marcus Tsohonis also scored 15. Kaleb Higgins led the way for the Roadrunners (10-17, 5-11) with 23 points and four assists. Corey Stephenson added 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
